### Key Changes
- **Padding increased to 16px**: More breathing room
- **Count badges**: Now pill-shaped with subtle background instead of plain text -- adds visual structure
- **Section title**: Slightly smaller (10.5px) with wider letter-spacing (0.06em) -- more refined uppercase treatment
- **Input focus state**: Teal border with teal-tinted glow ring -- consistent with accent color
- **Selected item**: Uses accent-subtle background and bold weight for better visibility
- **Hover on section headers**: Subtle background change makes collapsible sections feel interactive

---

## 6. Properties Panel (`PropertiesPanel.module.css`)

### Full Updated Styles

```css
.panel {
